OL,3,CIn pictures: The Artemis II moon
OL,4,Cmission
OL,6,FThe first astronauts to visit the moon
OL,7,Fin more than half a century landed
OL,8,Fsafely back on Earth on Friday night
OL,9,Finto Monday.
OL,11,FThe crew of four set records for space
OL,12,Fexploration, travelling further from
OL,13,FEarth than humans ever had before.
OL,15,FArtemis II's astronauts didn't land on
OL,16,Fthe Moon or orbit it, but instead,
OL,17,Fthey ducked behind its far side and
OL,18,Fcaptured views never before seen by
OL,19,Fthe human eye, along with a total
OL,20,Fsolar eclipse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
